#10201
Keywords:	mirror image spirit self
Name:	You
RoomDesc:$
You are standing here 

~
LookDesc:$
You look at the person standing before you. You note it's dress, it's
appearance and it's demeanor. It is you! The look on its face is the
definition of fury. It stares at you and slowly says, "^rI am every bit of hate
and anger you are and have ever had. I am every prejudice and fear you are and
have had. I am all the little secrets you keep from friends and family for
fear of being outcast. I am all that you attempt to hide and I will be denied
no longer. I will kill you, so that I may live!"^N 
~
