Name:	a Small Flame Wreathed Lizard
RoomDesc:$
A small red flame wreathed lizard hisses at you 

~
LookDesc:$
^RA small red lizard crawls about in front of you. It's body is wreathed in
brillant flame. Even though it is not touching you, the heat of it's body
begins to sear your  skin. It's miniscle dot-like eyes stare at you with an
unnerving intelligence and hatred. You get the distinct impression this thing
means to cook and devour your heart!^N 
~
