#10203
Keywords:	air elemental spirit element cloud
Name:	a Dark Lightning filled Cloud
RoomDesc:$
A dark lightning filled cloud hovers about you 

~
LookDesc:$
^cA dark cloud thunders nearby. Lightning shoots through it, slightly
illuminating it's interior momentarily with an evil reddish light. It circles
you constantly, darting towards you then veering off at an impossible angle.
Winds whip you as it passes, flaying your skin, chilling you to the bone and
tearing the very breath from your lungs. You believe you see shapes form in
the mist, horrifying, demonic images.^N 
~
