#10204
Keywords:	water elemental spirit element form
Name:	A Gigantic Humaniod Water Form
RoomDesc:$
A gigantic humaniod shaped water form floats here. 

~
LookDesc:$
^GA current sweeps by and begins to coalesce before you. It seems to be vaguely
human shaped, with a hulking body and head that appears to connect directly
with the body. It swells in size, taking in more volume from the sea around
it. It's maul opens and snatches lesser creatures in, swallowing them whole.
It's green eyes glow with a hellish and sickening light as it scans the deep
for more morsels. Suddenly, it fixes it gaze on you and emits a loud moan that
echoes through the depths and nearly shatters you eardrums. Apparently, it has
found it's next meal!^N 
~
