#10205
Keywords:	earth rock stone elemental spirit element
Name:	A Huge Stone Troll
RoomDesc:$
A huge stone troll stands here. 

~
LookDesc:$
^LA huge stone troll stands before you. It is fully 20 meters tall and half as
wide. It horns appear to be made of gold, shot through with ebony streaks. Its
skin is mottled, made of different types of rock and mineral, crystals and raw
gems encurst it's hide. Thick veins of molten lava can be seen oozing beneath
it's exterior. It's teeth, rusty jagged outcroppings of solid iron. It stares
at you, though it's dull smooth eyes of polished obsidian betray no emotion,
you feel the power of it's undying unquenchable anger!^N 
~
